        "maintext": "In 2012, UC Davis was named the \"coolest school\" in the US by the Sierra Club. The award celebrates environmental responsibility in categories like energy use, waste management, food sources, and education.",
        "pNames": [
          "UC Davis",
          "Stanford",
          "UC Irvine",
          "UC Berkeley"
        ],
        "pTexts": [
          "We drew praise for our 'well-rounded' environmental efforts, including bicycle infrastructure and waste diversion.",
          "Barely behind us in 3rd place, Stanford earned honors for its commitment to sustainable agriculture in class and cafeteria.",
          "Irvine was our closest UC competitor, noted for its many extracurricular environmental groups and recycling efforts.",
          "Berkeley ranked at 20th place, scoring surprisingly low in sustainability education and research."
        ],
